              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A LiF 500 mug/cm**2 thick target housed in a thin",
                "walled spherical scattering chamber. The LiF target was",
                "95% enriched in 6Li and evaporated on a 500 mug/cm**2",
                "thick Au backing. To minimize Li evaporation the target",
                "was cooled during the experiment and the gold backing",
                "was mounted towards the beam."
